# shared dictation config — sourced by dictation-{stop,toggle}
# single source of truth for model + engine.
#
# engine: whisper-cli from the whisper-cpp-rocm system package
# (~/flakes overlays/whisper-rocm.nix). On PATH after a system-switch.
